Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:44.33,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\an8}あの雲の彼方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:48.71,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\an8}私をつれていって
